title: DDFP 467: Best Fictional Football Players & 'Game of Thrones' recap
itunes:title: DDFP 467: Best Fictional Football Players & 'Game of Thrones' recap
description:
Shek is joined by Handsome Hank and Maurice Jones-Drew to discuss the finale episode of "Game of Thrones" and their final fantasy rankings for the season. Also, due to Shek and the guys being on vacation, producers Black Tie, Bartlett, Sully and EmmaVP start the show with an in-depth discussion of the all-time best fictional football players.
